''Zoids: The Battle Begins'' received generally positive reception from video game critics. Reviewers for ''[[Amtix]]'' praised the game, with one writer considered it to be one of the best on the Amstrad.<ref name=Amtix/> A writer for [[Crash (magazine)|''Crash'']] gave positive marks for its graphics and gameplay and called it one of the best titles on the ZX Spectrum.<ref name=Crash2/>

